title: Suki Waterhouse
summary: Alice Suki Waterhouse (born 5 January 1992) is an English model, actress and singer. She began a career in modelling at the age of 16, and she would go on to model for several major fashion labels. Her first feature film as an actress was a minor role in Pusher in 2012, and she has since appeared in films such as The Divergent Series: Insurgent, The Bad Batch, and Assassination Nation. In 2016, she co-founded the accessories brand Pop & Suki with Poppy Jamie and Leo Seigal.
